ing IP from DHCP server....."},{"pid":"327c61a7c05d97490890cdfb6c3bec796311a2c1","tid":410191,"uid":136476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新router睇下有無default開左wifi,用電話連返wifi入去set</blockquote><br />\n有試過用電話連wifi set<br />\n得signal 上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd800452f4a91a750d1fbb18b77b94fb0e15eb88","tid":410191,"uid":133986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新router睇下有無default開左wifi,用電話連返wifi入去set</blockquote><br />\n有試過用電話連wifi set<br />\n得signal 上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎你真係好入門級...用緊邊間上網?<br />\n如果你dhcp唔得應該係pppoe?<br />\n要入返login id同password"},{"pid":"1e8578bd0a6a8a30b6d4586216674ac3ddaa34fc","tid":410191,"uid":136476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7077160db4219a1a23817db90b52e8fefa36f4","tid":410191,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"電話set咪同電腦set一樣<br />\n咪又係連番個wifi開番個瀏覽器打番個ip入番個setting page"},{"pid":"153bc5c1cec289296912d9853a2af47027cb326d","tid":410191,"uid":136476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電話set咪同電腦set一樣<br />\n咪又係連番個wifi開番個瀏覽器打番個ip入番個setting page</blockquote><br />\n我知呀 但係我之前都set過 就係一直都淨係得信號上唔到網"},{"pid":"bac113c72e9b1243a8014720fd1a78b68ad74019","tid":410191,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電話set咪同電腦set一樣<br />\n咪又係連番個wifi開番個瀏覽器打番個ip入番個setting page</blockquote><br />\n我知呀 但係我之前都set過 就係一直都淨係得信號上唔到網</blockquote><br />\n咁你用緊咩公司咩寬頻<br />\n10m以下果啲vdsl就要ppoe login先上到<br />\n100m以上果啲就揀番DHCP/自動取得ip<br />\n呢啲嘢係internet&gt;wan果到set"},{"pid":"91deab9394165edcb9062fdc9553f7b24e3f02e7","tid":410191,"uid":136476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電話set咪同電腦set一樣<br />\n咪又係連番個wifi開番個瀏覽器打番個ip入番個setting page</blockquote><br />\n我知呀 但係我之前都set過 就係一直都淨係得信號上唔到網</blockquote><br />\n咁你用緊咩公司咩寬頻<br />\n10m以下果啲vdsl就要ppoe login先上到<br />\n100m以上果啲就揀番DHCP/自動取得ip<br />\n呢啲嘢係internet&gt;wan果到set</blockquote><br />\n100m hkbn"},{"pid":"f0a678b31d469b07d73b932193617c162ae95681","tid":410191,"uid":136476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新router睇下有無default開左wifi,用電話連返wifi入去set</blockquote><br />\n有試過用電話連wifi set<br />\n得signal 上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎你真係好入門級...用緊邊間上網?<br />\n如果你dhcp唔得應該係pppoe?<br />\n要入返login id同password</blockquote><br />\n係咪一定要一條線連router同牆身<br />\n另外一條router連電腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e35c3c85a8b3da8a70b55145476aa0f74ff4f7","tid":410191,"uid":133986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新router睇下有無default開左wifi,用電話連返wifi入去set</blockquote><br />\n有試過用電話連wifi set<br />\n得signal 上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎你真係好入門級...用緊邊間上網?<br />\n如果你dhcp唔得應該係pppoe?<br />\n要入返login id同password</blockquote><br />\n係咪一定要一條線連router同牆身<br />\n另外一條router連電腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔駛連電腦,首先<br />\n1.牆身條線插router wan port<br />\n2.睇下你部router wan燈有無著<br />\n3.入到setting畫面去wan/internet揀dhcp<br />\n確定你部router上到網先"},{"pid":"74ee219a95cc89a60f7c4d81c51414cfefcbd6a4","tid":410191,"uid":136476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新router睇下有無default開左wifi,用電話連返wifi入去set</blockquote><br />\n有試過用電話連wifi set<br />\n得signal 上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎你真係好入門級...用緊邊間上網?<br />\n如果你dhcp唔得應該係pppoe?<br />\n要入返login id同password</blockquote><br />\n係咪一定要一條線連router同牆身<br />\n另外一條router連電腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔駛連電腦,首先<br />\n1.牆身條線插router wan port<br />\n2.睇下你部router wan燈有無著<br />\n3.入到setting畫面去wan/internet揀dhcp<br />\n確定你部router上到網先</blockquote><br />\n冇着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得Wlan燈有着"},{"pid":"538078f121b9484b1c459e7eb73bb81334106f0e","tid":410191,"uid":147485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T19:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新router睇下有無default開左wifi,用電話連返wifi入去set</blockquote><br />\n有試過用電話連wifi set<br />\n得signal 上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎你真係好入門級...用緊邊間上網?<br />\n如果你dhcp唔得應該係pppoe?<br />\n要入返login id同password</blockquote><br />\n係咪一定要一條